<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>KHRIHFA RALKAP KAL U CH180</title>
<key>F</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Khrihfa ralkap mi hna, Dohnak ah kal u, Hmailei ah a kalmi Jesuh kha
 zoh u; Jesuh kan Siangpahrang, Hmaiah a kan sak, Raldoh zuam a kalmi,
 Jesuh kha zoh u,

[C1]
   Khrihfa ralkap mi hna, Ral dohnak ah kal, Hmailei ah a kalmi Jesuh
   kha zoh u.

[V2]
 Jesuh min an theih ah, Rulhreu mi an tli, Khrihfa ralkapmi nih, Teinak
 hmu u si, Aunak thawng an theih in, Rulhreu pennak rawk, U le nau au len
 u, Lawmhnak in thangthat.

[C2]
   Khrihfa ralkap mi hna, Ral dohnak ah kal, Hmailei ah a kalmi Jesuh
   kha zoh u.

[V3]
 Ralkap rian an tuan bang, Khrihfabu an tuah, Hmailei mithiang keneh,
 Kannih kan zulh hna, Kannih then lo in kawp, Pum khat te kan si, Dawtnak,
 zumhnak, bochannak, Kan lungtak a si.

[C3]
   Khrihfa ralkap mi hna, Ral dohnak ah kal, Hmailei ah a kalmi Jesuh
   kha zoh u.

[V4]
 Vawlei mi-lian pennak, An rawk len nain, Bawi Jesuh pennak kha,
 Zungzal a hmun ko, Rulhreu puarpennak kha, Teinak an hmu lo, Jesuh bia a
 kan kam, Amah bia a hmun.

[C4]
   Khrihfa ralkap mi hna, Ral dohnak ah kal, Hmailei ah a kalmi Jesuh
   kha zoh u.

[V5]
 Vawlei mi vialte hna, Lut Khrihfabu ah, Nan teinak hlasaknak, Nannih
 zong sa u; Rel cawk lo chan lakah, Van le vawlei mi, Thangthat le
 upatnak, Jesuh pe u si.

[C5]
   Khrihfa ralkap mi hna, Ral dohnak ah kal, Hmailei ah a kalmi Jesuh
   kha zoh u.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>180</hymn_number>
</song>